metadata.name: AMORE
metadata.description:
As she stared at herself in the full length mirror in her room. She thought for a moment, then frowned.  
There was only one thought on her mind: 
Why would Collins write to her about self love when he makes her feel alive?

He wrote her a two sentence note:

Dear Amore,

Try to be nicer to yourself,  
Be kind to yourself.

Love,  
Collins

In that moment, her heart fluttered a bit. She was caught off guard by the thought of she not finding happiness in herself but in him alone.
